          -# SUPER DIRTY: Must Clean Up Later
          %a{href: "#signup"}
            %button.primary Sign Up
%div{style: "padding: 80px 0px;"}
  .row
    .small-12.columns
      %hr{style: "position: relative; top: 80px; margin: 0px;"}
      .row
        .small-8.small-offset-2.columns
          %div{style: "background-color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center;"}
            %h4{style: "font-family: 'mergelight'; color: #666666;"} Walks are more than just a chance for your dog to do their business. Wag Wag gives dogs the fun time they crave while youâ€™re away, with the convenience you would expect from a modern service.
  .row{style: "text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;"}
    .small-12.medium-4.columns
      = image_tag "gps.svg", width: "70px"
      %h5{style: "font-family: 'Source Sans Pro'; color: #666666; margin-top: 20px;"} We enable a GPS locatable collar on all dogs we walk. This helps keep your best friend safe and gives you peace of mind.
    .small-12.medium-4.columns
      = image_tag "list.svg", width: "70px"
      %h5{style: "font-family: 'Source Sans Pro'; color: #666666; margin-top: 20px;"} We'll send you a list of your pet's activities to keep you informed. Want us to look out for something? Let us know!
    .small-12.medium-4.columns
      = image_tag "pic.svg", width: "70px"
      %h5{style: "font-family: 'Source Sans Pro'; color: #666666; margin-top: 20px;"} Say cheese! We'll send you a pic or video of your happy pup after every walk. We may even post it to Instagram.
%div#signup{style: "padding: 80px 0px; background-color: #3E4651"}
  .row
    .small-12.medium-6.columns
      %h2{style: "font-family: 'mergelight'; color: #ffffff;"} Sign up now to be included in our pre-launch special. 
      %h2{style: "font-family: 'mergelight'; color: #ffffff; margin-top: 30px;"} We'll be offering walks at discounted rate of <span style="color: #F16233">$8 each</span> for a limited number of new clients during our initial launch phase.
    .small-12.medium-5.columns
      = form_for (@user) do |f|
        .field{style: "font-family: 'mergelight';"}
          = f.label :email, "Email Address", style: "color: #ffffff;"
          = f.text_field :email
        .field.m-top-20{style: "font-family: 'mergelight';"}
          = f.label :first_name, "First Name", style: "color: #ffffff;"
          = f.text_field :first_name
        .field.m-top-20{style: "font-family: 'mergelight';"}
          = f.label :last_name, "Last Name", style: "color: #ffffff;"
          = f.text_field :last_name
        .field{style: "font-family: 'mergelight';"}
          = f.label :zip_code, "Zip Code", style: "color: #ffffff;"
          = f.text_field :zip_code
        .field{style: "font-family: 'mergelight';"}
          = f.label :phone, "Phone Number", style: "color: #ffffff;"
          = f.telephone_field :phone
        %p{style: "font-family: 'mergelight'; font-size: small;  color: #ffffff; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;"} We promise not to sell or use your info for anything besides business purposes and special Wag Wag offers.
        .actions
          %button.secondary Sign up
